&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-Assisted Content Creation:&lt;/strong&gt; Use GenAI tools (like ChatGPT, Claude, Midjourney, Jasper, or similar) to brainstorm, draft, and iterate on high-quality B2B content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Social Media Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Draft compelling copy, hooks, and visual prompts for paid and organic campaigns on &lt;strong&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Meta&lt;/strong&gt; (Facebook/Instagram).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content Scaling &amp;amp; Repurposing:&lt;/strong&gt; Turn long-form assets (webinars, whitepapers, case studies) into bite-sized social posts, carousels, and short-form video scripts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative Asset Prompting:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with design teams or use AI image generators to create eye-catching visuals and ad creatives that convert.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Tracking:&lt;/strong&gt; Monitor engagement metrics on LinkedIn and Meta to understand what content resonates and iterate based on data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
