&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education:&lt;/strong&gt; Currently pursuing a degree in Marketing, Communications, Journalism, Business, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Tool Fluency:&lt;/strong&gt; Hands-on experience with AI writing assistants, LLMs, or image generation tools for content creation (please showcase this in your application!).&lt;/li&gt;
